{"tid":1271923,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爆塊玻璃又話失民心 尋日黑警集會暴打前線同記者有無失市民心呀？","createTime":"2019-07-01T08:10:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T11:06:27.000Z","uid":252492,"like":109,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"953fb320a8c11517b4a207c36f60373c9a419f4b","tid":1271923,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T08:10:57.000Z","msg":"成班政治潔癖人講你有講，你班人點都唔會上前線<br />\n剩識跟大台遊行唱k, 永遠剩識留係橋上面影相<br />\n比政府操控傳媒話你好暴力就人講你又講<br />\n你班廢物唔係諗住要前線成世企係警犬前面做沙包比人任毆拿咩世界認同呀<br />\n你班政治潔癖既人顛完未？"},{"pid":"98de4b18029c498b1b51fbc2a049aa9e6875f805","tid":1271923,"uid":4050,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T08:11:16.000Z","msg":"共匪一貫手法，分化、滲透，然後拉籠一派打一派，屌嗰啲當然90%都係五毛，但亦都唔排除有真心膠中計信咗佢地一套，呢個就係拉籠一派打一派，群眾鬥群眾，要你自相殘殺，孤立主要敵人，民初時期國民政府分裂就係共匪搞出嚟，共匪玩咗咁多年分化，普羅大眾應該要熟悉呢一點，大家都係擁抱自由民主嘅價值，呢個要保持清醒，同伴之間要互相尊重，唔好咁易上五毛當"},{"pid":"05da30a3b22f921bb8609d20b27e34badb3a4088","tid":1271923,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T08:11:30.000Z","msg":"因為有cctvb"},{"pid":"612b11825efb914444d14ba1a225d7113229acc8","tid":1271923,"uid":137371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T08:11:53.000Z","msg":"唔支持既話唔出聲已經好夠"},{"pid":"c0fb0a5ad56a1f6692c66ab8d4c1f7cdcf1b7141","tid":1271923,"uid":252492,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T08:17:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cNUWMmb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcNUWMmb.jpg&h=43922baf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V125EGc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV125EGc.jpg&h=6db34aee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4gfSjGd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4gfSjGd.jpg&h=9ae0858a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/57ePmUz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F57ePmUz.jpg